    "language": "zhs",
    "review_level": "Professional",
    "content": "<p><strong>低加坡里</strong>的字面意思是&quot;十座城市&quot;。这个词指的是<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"186629\" data-resourceType=\"FIAKeyTerms\">加利利海</span>和<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"186590\" data-resourceType=\"FIAKeyTerms\">约旦河</span>以东的地区。住在那里的人大多数不是<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"186525\" data-resourceType=\"FIAKeyTerms\">犹太人</span>。</p>",
